To analyze sales performance, profitability, and discount impact through dynamic visuals and slicer-driven exploration.

This project focuses on transforming a validated Power BI data model into an interactive business dashboard. The dashboard simulates a real-world business intelligence report used by management to monitor performance and identify improvement opportunities.

ğŸ—‚ï¸ Dataset: 
Sample Superstore dataset (Kaggle)

